2.0 EXCAVATION MODULE (EM) - Technical Specifications

2.1 Mechanical System

Primary Mechanism: Dual Counter-Rotating Drum Assembly with Replaceable Teeth

```
Drum Diameter: 0.8 meters each
Drum Length: 2.4 meters
Rotation Speed: 5-15 RPM (variable based on regolith density)
Torque Capacity: 4500 NÂ·m per drum
